data.description: 3 bedroom, 2 bathrooms, 1316 sq. ft. Updated with Lifeproof luxury vinyl plank flooring. The kitchen has a pantry and breakfast bar. Updated cabinets/sink/faucet. Formal dining room and dining area by the kitchen. Master bedroom is separate from the others and has a walk-in closet. Master bathroom has a separate tub and shower. Wood burning fireplace in the main area. Fully fenced with RV gate and dog run. RV hookups. Storage shed with attached carport. Private well and septic. Well piping just replaced in September! Bring your horses!
